<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Dsignative About Us</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Ysabeau" rel="stylesheet" />
    <!-- Latest compiled JavaScript -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about_us_style.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('partials/nav-bar') %>

    <main>
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row" id="row1">
          <div class="col-3">
            <img class="purple" src="/images/purple.svg" />
          </div>
          <div class="col col-9">
            <div class="txt txt-1">
              <h2>Nice to meet you !</h2>
              <p>
                We are Maya, Raneem, Nour, and Joudy, co-founders of Deignative website.
                Our journey started when we were trying to find a multimedia specialists
                platforms and a place for those who are interested in looking for a
                talented designer. The rest is history !
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row" id="row2">
          <div class="col col-9">
            <div class="txt txt-2">
              <h2>Our Vision:</h2>
              <p>
                Our vision is to create a simple and user-friendly interface that bridges
                the gap between indie multimedia specialists and companies seeking the
                right talent. We believe that every talented individual, regardless of
                whether they hold a degree or not, deserves recognition and the
                opportunity to work with big corporations. By connecting these two worlds,
                we hope to make the process of finding and hiring a talented designer
                easier, faster, and more efficient for corporations. At the same time, we
                aim to help multimedia specialists showcase and sell their work, giving
                them the opportunity to reach a wider audience and land great
                opportunities with giant corporations. Our motivation is to facilitate
                profitability for both corporations and freelancers while creating a
                platform that fosters easier and more efficient communication. Designative
                is for anyone who is searching for a designer or looking for customers in
                the multimedia industry.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-3">
            <img class="white" src="/images/white.svg" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
